Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢對愛西亞那麼粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點出氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 一個狗屎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於我來說 可不想被你們惡魔殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
